{"tid":1423643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［新聯合陣線」是否需要重新正名「光復香港，時代革命」？","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:21:59.000Z","uid":230146,"like":20,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7d55d8fad3357ea8877d2a04679700cd7cdbed","tid":1423643,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"運動已經面臨崩潰邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n中共以扣港獨帽子，<br />\n加上用影響民生來分化反送中陣營，<br />\n定必分化到大中華主義者以及民生派既c奶大叔，<br />\n我地既最終目的係咩，大家心知肚明，<br />\n但事實上好多人仍然未覺得需要，<br />\n時機亦未到，<br />\n所以必須聯合多數人，繼續支持呢個運動落去，<br />\n唔想因為運動失焦、分化，路線鬥爭，鬥手段激進之下逐漸消亡，咁樣係好對唔住六位先烈同埋幾百個被捕人士。<br />\n首先既然對家扣港獨帽子，<br />\n就要重新定義「光復香港，時代革命」，<br />\n以達到多數人支持既新聯合陣線<br />\n大家有咩睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560c932282584f3e29c0a274a653bed4c121ccf7","tid":1423643,"uid":45123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"改下囉<br />\n光復香港 追究暴警"},{"pid":"9351060c859c28fed9a1007d70b99e2e6c2fa6fa","tid":1423643,"uid":230146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"560c932282584f3e29c0a274a653bed4c121ccf7","tid":1423643,"uid":45123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"改下囉<br />\n光復香港 追究暴警"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"唔要改字，但賦與新意義"},{"pid":"4b9cf2227809464db5f33c4abe6230457e09a5ca","tid":1423643,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f096ed031b740f5fe10257dbfe60d1c2743a88","tid":1423643,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset